sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Auth as Firebase Authentication
    participant DB as Firestore Database
    participant CF as Cloud Functions
    participant Storage as Firebase Storage
    participant FCM as Cloud Messaging (FCM)
    participant Contacts as Emergency Contacts
    participant App as Expo App

    Note over Auth, App: Authentication & Role Assignment
    Auth->>DB: Validate User Credentials
    DB-->>Auth: Return Role (User/Admin)
    Auth-->>App: Provide Access Token

    Note over Auth, App: Disaster Report Handling
    App->>DB: Submit Disaster Report
    DB->>CF: Trigger: OnCreate (New Report)
    CF->>DB: Set Initial Status = "Pending"
    CF->>FCM: Notify Nearby Users of New Entry

    Note over Auth, App: Media Association
    App->>Storage: Upload Media Files
    Storage-->>DB: Save & Map Media URL to Report ID

    Note over Auth, App: Voting & Verification Logic
    App->>DB: Submit Community Vote
    DB->>CF: Trigger: OnUpdate (Vote Count)
    rect rgb(240, 240, 240)
        Note right of CF: Business Logic
        CF->>CF: Evaluate Vote Threshold
        CF->>DB: Update Verification Status
    end
    CF->>FCM: Notify Users & Admin of Status Change

    Note over Auth, App: SOS Automation
    App->>DB: Store SOS Alert Event
    DB->>CF: Trigger: SOS Event
    CF->>Contacts: Dispatch Emergency Alerts (SMS/Push)
    CF->>FCM: Notify Admin of High-Priority Emergency

    Note over Auth, App: Data Cleanup & Sync
    DB->>CF: Trigger: OnDelete
    CF->>Storage: Remove Orphaned Media Files
    CF->>DB: Clean Up Database References
    DB-->>App: Stream Live Updates (Snapshot Listeners)